## Problem

The [Release #211 run](https://github.com/getsentry/craft/actions/runs/23569685060) shows 5 deprecation warnings about Node.js 20 actions. GitHub will force Node.js 24 starting June 2, 2026, and remove Node.js 20 on September 16, 2026.

